  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/a94bdfb895a8943a137b8a35c3932c7e.avif?t=1720856076\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>MIMIC is a puzzle-solving escape room atmospheric horror game in which you play against a creature that mimics your every single move. <br>Your task is extremely simple - escape the room ..... But is it <i>that </i> easy?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.poster.avif?t=1720856076\" width=412 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.webm?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.mp4?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It is a deeply connected web of puzzle and horror that keeps you invested to discover all the possible outcomes of a battle against your own <i>shadow</i>. With multiple endings and an intriguing hidden lore , it is the perfect game to test out your wits while experiencing a creepy setting.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/5227d1a01be1e7f54d73f439f88f3bdf.poster.avif?t=1720856076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/5227d1a01be1e7f54d73f439f88f3bdf.webm?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/a94bdfb895a8943a137b8a35c3932c7e.avif?t=1720856076\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>MIMIC is a puzzle-solving escape room atmospheric horror game in which you play against a creature that mimics your every single move. <br>Your task is extremely simple - escape the room ..... But is it <i>that </i> easy?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.poster.avif?t=1720856076\" width=412 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.webm?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/f43751946ff927d226a3f800d9e78ea7.mp4?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It is a deeply connected web of puzzle and horror that keeps you invested to discover all the possible outcomes of a battle against your own <i>shadow</i>. With multiple endings and an intriguing hidden lore , it is the perfect game to test out your wits while experiencing a creepy setting.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/5227d1a01be1e7f54d73f439f88f3bdf.poster.avif?t=1720856076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961970/extras/5227d1a01be1e7f54d73f439f88f3bdf.webm?t=1720856076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
